        "TileImage": "$($repository 6e1a5791-47f2-4435-ad3a-217eaf539d1f).Image",
        "Description": "Where are these people hiding?\r\rWelcome to Isla de H&apos;n&apos;S! \r(Isle of Hide and Seek, for those who don&apos;t get it.)\r\rThese five contestants have chosen to play the game and YOU are the seeker! Find them, eliminate them and gain the fifty-thousand dollar prize reward at the nearest Providence-branded ATM!\r\rAvoid collateral damage because they aren&apos;t playing the game. If there&apos;s collateral, the game is over.  Be stealthy, too! \r\rIt&apos;s Hide and Seek for a reason. \r\rHave fun!",
